title: There’s No Place Like Home at Edina Park Apartments
posting_body: ['Welcome home!', 'Schedule a Tour!', 'Book an appointment online at 2tour.site/OHB/NJQI', 'At Edina Park apartments we have one, two, and three-bedroom apartment homes that overlook natural wetlands located near a walking and bike path.', "You'll enjoy our outdoor swimming pool with sundeck, Party Room with catering kitchen, on-site laundry center, and heated underground parking.", 'We welcome dogs and cats and fiber-optic internet is available!', 'Visit today and see why you will love to call Edina Park home!', 'Home Amenities', 'Wall air conditioning', 'Appliances in kitchen', 'Ceiling fan', 'Fiber-optic internet service available', 'Smoke free', 'Window coverings', 'Community Amenities', 'Nearby walking & bike trails', 'Swimming pool', 'Party room', 'Laundry facility', 'Off street parking', 'Pet friendly - some restrictions apply', 'Fitness center', '24 hour emergency maintenance', 'Edina Park Apartments Information', 'Address:', '4480 Parklawn Ave, Edina MN, 55435', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Details/?pid=3', 'Deposit:', '$500', 'Application Fee:', '$45', 'Pet Fee:', '$100 - 400 (Note: Varies By Number & Type Of Pet(s))', 'Pet Deposit:', '$200 - 400 (Note: Varies By Number & Type Of Pet(s))', 'Office Hours', 'Monday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Tuesday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Wednesday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Thursday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Friday:', '9:00AM - 5:00PM', 'Saturday:', '11:00AM - 4:00PM', 'Sunday:', '11:00AM - 4:00PM']
